============================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                         |NAME           |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |LIMIT                            |               |5       |3           |
|1 |└─SUBPLAN SCAN                   |ANONYMOUS_VIEW1|5       |3           |
|2 |  └─SORT                         |               |5       |3           |
|3 |    └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE FULL SCAN|T1             |5       |2           |
============================================================================
